      "height": 320,
      "visible": true,
      "showLabel": true,
      "data": {
        "markdown": "# Skill: PortCompatibilityChecks\n\n**Category:** Validation Skill\n\n**Intent:** Prevent invalid or meaningless connections between nodes.\n\nPorts are contracts. This skill enforces them.\n\nThis graph is the contract.",
