      "visible": true,
      "showLabel": true,
      "data": {
        "markdown": "## Scope\n\n### This skill:\n- Validates proposed or existing edges\n- Checks port existence\n- Checks direction and semantic compatibility\n- Emits validation results\n\n### This skill does NOT:\n- Mutate graph topology\n- Modify ports\n- Modify edges\n- Guess intent",
